	(text "K9 and K10 select the internal calibration source \nfor right and left channel.\n\nDefault relay state selects DC_REF_2V5.\nActive relay state selects DAC OUTR/OUTL.\n\nCAL_NSource_R and CAL_NSource_L are tied to AGND \nbecause both calibration sources are single-ended.\n\nCAL_SRC_SEL controls both left and right calibration source relays.\n\nRelay OFF / CAL_SRC_SEL LOW  → DC_REF_2V5 selected\nRelay ON  / CAL_SRC_SEL HIGH → DAC OUTR/OUTL selected\n\nRelay coils are driven with low-side NMOS switches.\nCR7 and CR8 are flyback diodes."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 177.8 77.724 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.905 1.905)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "23dd70e9-4758-44ce-9ee0-007e692a6f23")
	)
	(text "ADR4525 provides the internal 2.5 V DC calibration source.\n\nThe actual DC_REF_2V5 voltage is measured with a calibrated DMM \nand stored in software as the calibration constant.\n\nR77 is a 0 Ω link between the reference output and the calibration source net.\nC88 is DNP and reserved for optional additional output filtering."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 27.178 178.816 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.905 1.905)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "82235841-0345-4c2a-99e9-de076501b241")
	)
	(text "DAC / DC calibration source selection"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 56.896 20.574 0)
		(effects
